Package com.flipfit.constants

Class SQLConstants

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.constants.SQLConstants
public class SQLConstants extends Object
This class defines SQL queries used throughout the application for interacting with the database. The constants represent various SQL statements for operations like insert, update, and select on tables like FlipFitGym, FlipFitSlots, FlipFitUser, FlipFitGymOwner, and FlipFitBookings.
